These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, writing, sudoku
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, spy, crime, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, skateboarding, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, tram, subway, car
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
 2. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
 5. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
 6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person driving the tram and the person who's sport is basketball##2
 9. the person driving the car is the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
11. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
13. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
14. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person driving the subway##1
15. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person who's sport is basketball##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | chess     | magic-tricks   | sudoku | writing |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | fantasy   | musical   | crime  |
| Sport         | basketball  | skateboarding  | sailing  | volleyball |
| Transport     | boat    | subway | tram     | car    |

