.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, almond-milk, tea, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, artichoke, pear, kiwi
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, classical, punk, pop
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, pony, goat, hedgehog
 1. the fan of punk is between the owner of the chinchilla and the fan of classical##2
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
 4. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
 6. the person eating kiwi is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 7. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 8. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of hip-hop is the owner of the pony##1
10. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
11. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the fan of punk##8
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person eating artichoke##5
14. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
15. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
17. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the fan of classical##8
18. the person eating artichoke is not to the right of the owner of the pony##8
19. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | coffee | tea | soy-milk  | almond-milk  |
| Food          | kiwi     | artichoke | cranberry | pear  |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | punk  | pop | hip-hop |
| Pet           | goat | hedgehog | chinchilla    | pony  |

