 3. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the fan of dubstep##5
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person watching romance movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the person watching zombie movies##8
 7. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
11. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the fan of soul##8
