 3. the person eating apricot is the teacher##1
 4. the person eating spinach is between the police-officer and the paramedic##2
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person eating spinach##8
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the videographer##1
10. the paramedic is the person who's sport is swimming##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
12. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
14. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
15. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an odd position##4

