The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, punk, metal, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, badminton, golf, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, scooter, jet-ski, car
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 3. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the car##5
 4. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##8
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
10. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the fan of punk##8
11. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea   | fanta     | almond-milk    | juice |
| Music-Genre   | rock  | disco      | metal     | punk     |
| Sport         | cricket | golf  | sailing     | badminton  |
| Transport     | subway     | jet-ski | car | scooter     |

