.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, coffee, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, photography, traveling, camping
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, classical, techno, country
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch, pakistani, colombian
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the colombian##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
 3. the person drinking milk is the fan of classical##1
 4. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 5. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the fan of hip-hop##8
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
 9. the dutch is not to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##8
10. the fan of techno is not the egyptian##6
11. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
12. the colombian is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
13. the fan of country is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
14. the egyptian is on the right of the fan of techno##1

