 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking water##1
 7. the analyst is not to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##8
 8. the software-developer is on the far right##1
 9. the security-guard is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
10. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
13. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the analyst##8

