.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, traveling, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, fisherman, police-officer, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, musical, crime, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, salsa, funk, blues
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the freelancer##8
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
 4. the security-guard is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the police-officer##6
 6. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the fan of salsa##8
 7. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the police-officer##8
 8. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
 9. the fan of funk is in an even position##4
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
11. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the police-officer and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | fishing    | traveling   | gardening   | rock-climbing |
| Job           | freelancer | fisherman    | police-officer | security-guard    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | satire | musical     | martial-arts    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b   | funk      | salsa         | blues     |

 